{"tid":744314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【世盃終極戰】老翁馬會買波嫌職員填錯飛 揮拳施襲斥：乜你咁X蠢","createTime":"2018-07-16T00:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T01:34:06.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84fa91f330efb93bb6d126a815467bd0c2cddd42","tid":744314,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:38:53.000Z","msg":"經過長達一個月的比賽後，今屆俄羅斯世界盃終於來到最後一個比賽日，有波迷趁機趕緊投注，但有人疑因填寫彩票問題出手打傷職員！晚上9時許，比賽仍未開始，一名老翁便前往油麻地上海街的馬會投注站買波，並要求職員協助「填飛」，其間懷疑二人之間溝通出錯，老翁責怪職員「填錯飛」，又直斥「乜你咁X蠢」，未幾更情緒激動，揮拳向職員襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n職員頭部受傷，其他馬會職員見狀即上前制止，惟該名波迷趁亂其間逃去無蹤。警員接報到場調查，受傷職員需要送院治理，警方正追緝在逃的老翁。"},{"pid":"d113c7499a743ccd192328794debc0fb4c6e19c2","tid":744314,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d72decd0e16d7f0c4dec2cf2717e2da0f843eb2","tid":744314,"uid":13740,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:41:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚醒自己填<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67af0be231f21c8031f5cf175f94b2055b5d190a","tid":744314,"uid":41524,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:43:47.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n告到佢仆街要佢臨老過唔到世"},{"pid":"b2c8f9e7b6377ded62232d22dc5627455f591bbc","tid":744314,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:45:03.000Z","msg":"字都唔撚識咪仲蠢<br />\n飛都要人幫手填<br />\n洗唔洗人幫你除埋褲痾尿呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e61904d64f2facac4fdc45bc9607402f6a2a5f2","tid":744314,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T00:54:18.000Z","msg":"飛都唔識填機又唔識用邊個蠢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src